about__text:
Experience luxury living at “ECO Sergeli”, “Muhtrasham” and many more properties of Grover

Grover is a modern real estate development company located in Tashkent, Uzbekistan. The development features a variety of residential properties, including apartments, villas and commercial properties such as shops, warehouses and production plants.

Grover is located in the booming area of Tashkent, and is close to popular landmarks such as the biggest Auto showrooms of world famous brands as well as one and only in Central Asia underground.

The development is known for its high-quality construction and amenities, including parks, children playgrounds, parking zones and modern infrastructure.
